Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.17,0:04:34.99,title,NTP,0,0,0,,简称OK大作战（暂）{\fad(1300,0)}{\pos(520,415)}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.97,0:00:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事? 祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.52,0:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古文辞典?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.93,0:00:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.01,0:00:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.44,0:00:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.54,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要借其它什么东西吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.69,0:00:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.90,0:01:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.62,0:01:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 花寺学院的学园祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.10,0:01:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年莉莉安学生会也会有人来帮忙的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.81,0:01:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照理是这样的 怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然预定是第二学期过来商量相关事项
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.65,0:01:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在这之前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.90,0:01:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能…先见个面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 没有什么大事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.46,0:01:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为企划得差不多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.61,0:01:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想先打探一下莉莉安那边能够帮上多少忙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.01,0:01:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是很重要的事吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.73,0:01:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你呀 该不会是被学长们当跑腿的使唤了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.30,0:01:49.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的学生会长是个什么样的人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.04,0:01:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候即使你不愿意也会知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛 嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.41,0:02:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不方便的话拒绝也不要紧的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.37,0:02:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先以参加为前提来讨论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.30,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没和黄蔷薇大人商量之前也得不到什么结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.76,0:02:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不是祥子同学吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.18,0:02:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.03,0:02:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人的事 总不能和她本人商量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.34,0:02:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.36,0:02:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿过高大的校门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.43,0:02:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让裙子上的褶痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让白色的水手领翻起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓地行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事还用得着多想吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.95,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连络了令大人的话 由乃同学必然也会跟来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 把人说得像金鱼粪一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.39,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}金鱼粪:日语中用来形容跟屁虫的词语 因为金鱼的粪总是拖着长长的一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.14,0:05:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岂止是像而已 根本就是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.74,0:05:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现我要出门之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.91,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就缠着我问「去哪儿」 「和谁见面」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.25,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因为听说要见祐巳同学才跟来的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是想和小令一起出门呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:13.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就算是这么回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯~ 这说法真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.10,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小令你这个大笨蛋!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.03,0:05:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃同学是金鱼粪的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底该算是什么的粪呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 应该算是目高鱼之类的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.72,0:05:32.47,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}目高鱼:体型小眼睛突出 身长约3cm 是日本最小的淡水鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那么说我是目高鱼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多进入正题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如我在电话里所说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.32,0:05:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和花寺学院的人见面这件事我觉得应该接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 的确如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.38,0:05:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得差不多到了该准备对策的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.06,0:05:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是新人 还没搞清楚状况…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门见山地说 是指祥子大人有厌男症的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.82,0:06:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇大人她?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不怎么吃惊嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜女子高中有一两个这样的人也不奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.16,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以去花寺帮忙的话会有障碍是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.78,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子真是一点就通呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子她去年和前年都东躲西逃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有去参加那边的学园祭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.72,0:06:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那时她还是花蕾 所以大家就睁只眼闭只眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此祐巳想了个办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.47,0:06:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命名为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为避免突然被丢进男子学校受到严重刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而用逐渐适应的办法来克服厌男症的大作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.93,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为作战名是不是有点长过头了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.31,0:07:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说趁着暑假里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先让她逐渐习惯花寺的学生会成员们?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.00,0:07:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.97,0:07:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道为何祥子大人与我弟弟相处并没有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.37,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以尽早碰个面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我弟弟陪在旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持续给她灌输「这个人是安全的」这样的信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就能渐渐习惯男孩子了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.19,0:07:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么应该以什么样的方式见面呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是想要商量这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.57,0:07:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人的话不喜欢的活动一般不会参加的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.07,0:07:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能选山百合会和花寺学生会双方都在也不会不自然的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装成不期而遇的样子碰面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.12,0:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着还要制造成没办法逃避的局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.83,0:07:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么在哪里碰面比较好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.96,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡厅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.26,0:07:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学的家里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以 但是我家太小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆大家一起到祥子的家里去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.76,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 该怎么把花寺那边的人带过来呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.83,0:08:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让柏木同学帮忙怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.62,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柏木同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.07,0:08:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子的表哥兼未婚夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院的前学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.09,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请柏木同学带着学生会后辈们到祥子大人家里拜访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以什么名义呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.89,0:08:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的家里 没有可供大家聚会的地方之类的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.73,0:08:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来好像行得通呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那就这么决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.54,0:08:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拜托你和柏木同学交涉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想像中的…还要大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.53,0:09:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.27,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…有点想回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.24,0:09:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不太好吧 福泽家的姐弟俩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没猜错的话 这个袋子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装的是Maple Parlour的果冻精选礼盒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.17,0:09:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我最爱吃的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~ 好想吃啊~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有人能带着这个作为见面礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.99,0:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然造访我家呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.12,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵…贵安 柏木同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.25,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 柏木学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天突然登门拜访…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.49,0:10:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样坦率点多好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 祐巳和小麒都快进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.27,0:10:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找我有何贵干?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.73,0:10:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 事情是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.12,0:11:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在文化祭之前想先和莉莉安学生会的人碰个面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.92,0:11:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以能否拜托柏木同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.56,0:11:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着花寺学生会的各位去祥子大人家中拜访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们也「偶然」前去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.83,0:11:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是让小祥锻炼免疫力的作战吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 已经不必了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.13,0:11:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于柏木同学来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.72,0:11:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要「为学弟们提供宽敞场地」这样的正当理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.85,0:11:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在这么宽敞的豪宅里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.90,0:11:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就没有特意跑到小笠原家去的理由了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.74,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…真没意思~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.53,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是祐巳大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我弟弟祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.94,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院二年级的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.19,0:12:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是莉莉安女学园高中一年级的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫松平瞳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老姐平时承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.07,0:12:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子是柏木同学的表妹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.08,0:12:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样没错吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.25,0:12:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 三个人在这里密谈些什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,密谈?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.50,0:12:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是弟弟他有点事找柏木同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我只是陪他过来而已…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.57,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,归根究底 是有关祥子大人的事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错 真有趣啊祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.13,0:12:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那张想着什么都一目了然的脸实在是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小麒虽然也有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.13,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是祐巳别有一番独特的风味啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.88,0:13:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没闲到要四处宣扬这些有的没的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.35,0:13:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里遇到祐巳大人的事我不会外传的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.66,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是上次造成你和祥子大人吵架的元凶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳子她真的不会告诉祥子大人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.48,0:13:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.12,0:13:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.07,0:13:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.24,0:13:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩挺可爱的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.22,0:13:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦~~~?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 总觉得像幼儿园小朋友的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.05,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒喜欢的是哪种类型的女孩呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的女孩…吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么祐巳你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.12,0:14:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮而且头脑也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.33,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面看起来可能性格有点别扭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但实际上内心温柔 然后有点洁癖…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说啦 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.78,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是在说祥子学姐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.14,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.38,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让祥子大人克服厌男症的大作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.85,0:14:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简称OK大作战 需要重新考虑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.27,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 从莉莉安学园正门走出来时偶然相遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小林说的这种简单的作战也许也不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确定大家在莉莉安集合的日期后 就请告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会在莉莉安的附近等候时机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 小林同学你这趟来得真是时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻而易举就把计划定下了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.31,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也很期待着和山百合会的各位见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会排除万难 尽力配合你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.51,0:15:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小林同学 千万小心别冒犯了祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可要和大家交代清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让她的厌男症变本加厉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.91,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没法到花寺的学园祭帮忙了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.83,0:15:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种高岭之花 像公主一般的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是只敢从远处遥望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.77,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.74,0:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.31,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就要看祐麒的演技了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.16,0:16:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 和山百合会的各位突然遇见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.93,0:16:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.22,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃? 啊…啊啊…我…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.52,0:16:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方真是巧遇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去喝杯茶怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正巧我们学生会的成员也全在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.92,0:16:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就像这样 大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.35,0:16:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个感觉 OK大作战开始执行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了执行作战的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.12,0:16:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.88,0:17:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…贵安 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.51,0:17:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来得早了点 还以为不会遇见什么人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.46,0:17:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是图书馆的开放日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.93,0:17:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手提包里是我前些时间借的书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.53,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 祐巳该不会也是为了去图书馆而早来的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会突然遇见祥子大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人肯定连做梦都想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.30,0:17:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的妹妹会在策划着几小时之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.73,0:17:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把花寺的学生和自己凑在一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.26,0:17:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是 我弟弟他怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.26,0:18:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 听优提到过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.41,0:18:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒他是花寺的学生会成员吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该只是协助帮忙的程度而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.91,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.94,0:18:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事情想让你这做姐姐的事先知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.49,0:18:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到莉莉安的学园祭时 会拜托祐麒来帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:30.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人 已经计划好指定祐麒过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.43,0:18:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量避免陌生的男人接近的作战了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.27,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也准备演舞台剧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.25,0:18:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经这么定好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.56,0:18:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于去年我抵制参加所有和花寺的讨论会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.98,0:18:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连姐姐们让优同学来演王子一角都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.12,0:18:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果导致了大混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年这样安排就可以放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.95,0:19:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 这样就掉以轻心了可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深谋远虑的学姐们虽然已经毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有妹妹们在暗中图谋不轨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.74,0:19:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然到九月时会正式进行书面形式的委托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.71,0:19:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.94,0:19:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先委婉地和祐麒说一声吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.58,0:19:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年正是因为优的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.61,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳才成了我的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 姐姐大人 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.62,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才怎么了? 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才好像有什么话要说的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.50,0:20:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 要是在这里坦白了就什么都白费了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 突然一时想不起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.10,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.72,0:20:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.69,0:20:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了凉的湿手巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.92,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露在外边看起来很热的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.89,0:20:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣母玛莉亚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.71,0:21:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在企图欺骗祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.30,0:21:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.85,0:21:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.70,0:21:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是…无法瞒着姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就打电话给祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.43,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托他拒绝花寺那边的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.46,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请原谅我 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么骗啊瞒啊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.13,0:21:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事我完全理解不了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺那边怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.41,0:21:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把来龙去脉好好交代清楚 祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.42,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.21,0:22:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一五一十地告诉您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里太热了 到树荫下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.48,0:22:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.53,0:22:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.41,0:22:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我了解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.55,0:22:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么又向我坦白了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微再努力忍耐一会就成功了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.91,0:22:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这么做了 姐姐大人会怎么反应呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.82,0:22:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.41,0:22:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小伎俩我立刻就能看穿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.73,0:22:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会很生气吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.70,0:22:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会歇斯底里地大发雷霆呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.75,0:22:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可能会拿手绢当出气筒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.12,0:22:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辟哩啪啦地把它撕个粉碎吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.55,0:22:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.11,0:22:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太可怕了 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.04,0:22:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.21,0:23:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是生气 也仍然会参加会面的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.75,0:23:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把生气了的心情透过行为释放出来之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以保持住心理的平衡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.36,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.78,0:23:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歇斯底里其实是撒娇性质的自我保护罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.67,0:23:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为知道祐巳和令…还有山百合会的伙伴们会原谅我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.71,0:23:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能毫无顾虑地发脾气啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.28,0:23:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是为了我着想而采取的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.94,0:23:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在知道这一点的前提下生气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你们所做的并不见得是个坏主意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.40,0:23:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着我让我与花寺学生会见面这个作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.39,0:23:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.89,0:23:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很像水野蓉子大人她们会用的手段吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.44,0:23:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我可不是蓉子大人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.72,0:23:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.05,0:23:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.18,0:24:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是希望姐姐大人能以自己的意愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和花寺的各位会面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.70,0:24:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己的…意愿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.23,0:24:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.46,0:24:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不执行什么奇怪的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.68,0:24:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不了多久姐姐大人也能自行克服这个困难的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.17,0:24:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有时候真是让人吃惊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.88,0:24:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你能如此融洽地和我相处呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.03,0:24:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融洽…吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.47,0:24:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不可思议呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.93,0:24:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明和蓉子大人完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.67,0:24:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何我却会因你的言语行动变得愉快起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.86,0:25:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您原谅我了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.21,0:25:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.61,0:25:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预谋瞒着我的这件事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.92,0:25:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.35,0:25:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是未遂了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.61,0:25:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万分感谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.52,0:25:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这件事就算取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.33,0:25:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给祐麒打个电话告诉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.67,0:25:28.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了三点钟碰头的 现在应该还在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.09,0:25:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三点开始到山百合会的集会结束为止的时间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:32.66,0:25:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预定让他们在这附近等候的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.98,0:25:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:36.69,0:25:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:40.41,0:25:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是有一个提案…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.74,0:25:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.93,0:26:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.97,0:26:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么预定吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:16.14,0:26:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.38,0:26:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 请用茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.21,0:26:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子的家里喝麦茶的时候还加奶油的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.64,0:26:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.29,0:26:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然早了点 今天就到此为止吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:43.24,0:26:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…现在就结束?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:46.93,0:26:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:49.11,0:26:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的工作正好也告一个段落了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:52.74,0:26:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就收拾一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.06,0:26:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:07.13,0:27:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人在为等在大太阳下的祐麒他们着想呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:13.88,0:27:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们俩才知道的秘密 可真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.30,0:27:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.32,0:27:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学长们给的慰劳品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:28.77,0:27:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些学长们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.02,0:27:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在附近的咖啡厅里舒服地乘凉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.58,0:27:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按计划看到大小姐们之后 我来发出暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.01,0:27:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.78,0:27:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话千万不能露出马脚哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.47,0:27:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是你今天的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:44.57,0:27:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.60,0:27:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.45,0:27:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 比预定时间提前了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.34,0:27:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.43,0:28:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:04.03,0:28:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:05.66,0:28:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.45,0:28:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.48,0:28:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:13.30,0:28:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 祥子同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.51,0:28:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.70,0:28:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 祐麒同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.43,0:28:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…呃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:39.08,0:28:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方真是巧遇呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.37,0:28:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.32,0:28:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 方便的话去喝杯茶怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.68,0:28:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正巧我们学生会的成员也全在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.98,0:28:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本打算这么说下去的吧 这下该如何是好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.88,0:28:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…已经不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.15,0:29:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦~~?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.93,0:29:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.97,0:29:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳你都泄露给祥子大人了却不告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:08.92,0:29:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不是说要骗过敌人要先骗过自己人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.80,0:29:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认输了吗? 祐麒同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:18.68,0:29:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 真是一败涂地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.05,0:29:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come here~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.76,0:29:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.50,0:29:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.94,0:29:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是花寺的学员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.31,0:29:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.56,0:29:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 我有点不舒服…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.74,0:29:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.03,0:29:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇大人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.25,0:29:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 不要紧吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:55.98,0:29:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~~ 姐姐大人 振作一点啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:59.79,0:30:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.28,0:30:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不好了不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.13,0:30:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}祥子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.13,0:30:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊~~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.34,0:30:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 今天可要好好地把见面会坚持到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.21,0:30:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳尽量待在祥子身边 尽力协助她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.01,0:30:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.15,0:30:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也要努力营造和谐的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.70,0:30:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.69,0:30:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.16,0:30:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子 茶水方面由你负责
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.78,0:30:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.90,0:30:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 放学后再次集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.21,0:30:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的各位已经到了 正等着我们过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.36,0:30:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.28,0:30:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 我会尽量陪在你身边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:54.47,0:30:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.75,0:31:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.51,0:31:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.62,0:31:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.68,0:31:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:45.24,0:31:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧张的程度 对方肯定更胜一筹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.18,0:31:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安是我们的主场 姐姐大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.94,0:32:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎花寺学院高中的各位光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.00,0:32:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家不要拘束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.75,0:32:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:15.58,0:32:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.08,0:32:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢各位今天远道而来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.70,0:32:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自我介绍之前 请容我先向各位道个歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.05,0:32:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次因我身体不适导致见面会没有开成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.39,0:32:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是十分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.63,0:32:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在身体感觉怎么样?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.53,0:32:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托各位的福 已经完全没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.17,0:32:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是中暑吧 我不太适应夏天的气候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.51,0:32:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人正努力着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.01,0:33:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来 从花寺这边开始自我介绍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.60,0:33:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按年龄顺序来吧 祐麒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.08,0:33:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 先从日光学长开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.08,0:33:07.03,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:日光和月光分别是对药师寺昌光和药师寺朋光两兄弟的称呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:15.63,0:33:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺学院高中三年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.28,0:33:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是药师寺昌光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.42,0:33:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样三年级 我是药师寺朋光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.81,0:33:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 请问是双胞胎吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.24,0:33:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.17,0:33:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.44,0:33:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级 我叫高田铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.65,0:33:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是健身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.97,0:33:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健…健身?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.77,0:33:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:48.13,0:33:52.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的食物是 鸡胸肉和蛋白质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.85,0:33:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高田同学不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.15,0:33:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不注意气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.70,0:34:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个 小林 轮到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.74,0:34:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是二年级的小林正念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.31,0:34:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿手的科目是数学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.97,0:34:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不拿手的科目是除了数学之外的全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.16,0:34:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 稍微恢复了一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.20,0:34:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫有栖川…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:26.23,0:34:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是二年级学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.00,0:34:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样也是二年级 我是福泽祐麒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.73,0:34:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来老姐承蒙各位关照了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.23,0:34:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然很像祐巳同学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.17,0:34:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.22,0:34:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉安女学园高中部三年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:56.99,0:34:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小笠原祥子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:59.37,0:35:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山百合会里的通称是红蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.77,0:35:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.58,0:35:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山百合会就是指学生会吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.36,0:35:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是红蔷…什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.09,0:35:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很难记啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.51,0:35:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的各位并没有必要勉强这么叫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:28.54,0:35:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姓也好名也好 请随意称呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这可方便多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:36.79,0:35:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳同学 别吓唬人家啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.89,0:35:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我可不想姐姐大人被亲热地叫成祥子 小祥之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:44.38,0:35:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉~ 真是真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.53,0:35:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的 我是被称为黄蔷薇的支仓令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.16,0:35:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是久仰大名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.51,0:35:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于我的什么事情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.43,0:35:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中本领高超的女剑士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:59.03,0:36:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的剑道部里也有人说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.68,0:36:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分希望能和支仓同学切磋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:05.82,0:36:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说想亲身体验一下从正面而来的脸部攻击之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:13.57,0:36:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可真是不敢当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.28,0:36:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是二年级的藤堂志摩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.49,0:36:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通称白蔷薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:26.39,0:36:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是小寓寺的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:29.98,0:36:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前 贵寺住持曾来过我们学校演讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.80,0:36:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他讲得可真有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.12,0:36:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个体育馆的人都笑翻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.38,0:36:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知他的女儿在莉莉安就读后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.64,0:36:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很是期待能见上一面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.89,0:36:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…家父真是失礼了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.44,0:36:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二年级的福泽祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:58.93,0:37:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时担任红蔷薇花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.95,0:37:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.48,0:37:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那位福泽祐麒的亲姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.92,0:37:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹算是吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.97,0:37:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹是什么意思嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.64,0:37:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 这样下去会变成说姐弟相声的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.92,0:37:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.41,0:37:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是二年级担任黄蔷薇花蕾的岛津由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.78,0:37:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前已经做过自我介绍的支仓令的表妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.86,0:37:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这边可是地地道道的表姐妹哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:50.65,0:37:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被由乃同学嘴上占了便宜了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.12,0:37:55.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是担心这些的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.32,0:37:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一年级的二条乃梨子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.01,0:38:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣是鉴赏佛像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:02.90,0:38:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛像?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.36,0:38:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个我们学校也有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.70,0:38:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,学园祭的时候要顺便看看吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.40,0:38:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.60,0:38:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.74,0:38:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如在花祭的时候登场的那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.61,0:38:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是诞生佛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.86,0:38:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上天下 唯我独尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.43,0:38:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.61,0:38:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人 看起来能顺利过关了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.08,0:38:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.00,0:38:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于请莉莉安的各位帮忙的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.22,0:38:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让三位蔷薇大人担任活动的评委兼颁奖嘉宾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.89,0:38:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,评委和颁奖嘉宾是指?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:54.12,0:38:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年的主要活动是花寺合战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:58.24,0:38:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合战?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.77,0:39:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的学生们分为运动社团和文化社团两大阵营
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.00,0:39:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运用智慧和体力进行对战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.70,0:39:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了就是进行一些比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:09.76,0:39:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 评委要做些什么呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.73,0:39:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责判断比赛中智力问答的答案对错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.01,0:39:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有颁奖嘉宾呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:23.08,0:39:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给表现出色的团体或者个人颁发奖品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:28.51,0:39:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖品?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.22,0:39:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是下个月举行的莉莉安学园祭的门票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.71,0:39:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为莉莉安的学园祭没有票是无法入场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.56,0:39:44.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以每年山百合会都会把门票当作礼物带过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.84,0:39:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.95,0:39:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位听明白了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.57,0:39:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.78,0:39:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 各位蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.65,0:39:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能接受担任评委和颁奖嘉宾的请求吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.42,0:40:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.59,0:40:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.68,0:40:06.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:07.17,0:40:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.16,0:40:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于顺利地结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.57,0:40:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 如果没有什么其它问题的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.50,0:40:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我提议就这么结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.94,0:40:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 学园祭以外的事可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.31,0:40:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.08,0:40:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 有点小事请问有栖川同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.50,0:40:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.32,0:40:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我似乎听漏了您的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.44,0:40:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了联络上的方便 我觉得还是问清楚为好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.50,0:41:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃梨子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.20,0:41:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是不方便回答的事情吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.35,0:41:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.83,0:41:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.83,0:41:11.60,reference,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}注:爱丽丝（アリス）取自有栖川（アリスカワ）这个姓氏的前三个假名音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.03,0:41:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.18,0:41:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有栖川…金太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.97,0:41:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得不协调对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.61,0:41:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面自我介绍时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.37,0:41:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会惹大家发笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:33.52,0:41:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.83,0:41:41.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.36,0:41:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.16,0:42:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝是你的昵称吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.78,0:42:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金太郎这个名字虽然也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.98,0:42:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但爱丽丝这个名字听起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.74,0:42:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太适合你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.69,0:42:36.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子…大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.64,0:42:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不幸错生为男儿之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.79,0:42:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我多么希望能被生为女孩 进莉莉安就读啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:58.84,0:43:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…成为祥子大人的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.79,0:43:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…然后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:04.81,0:43:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我慢着!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:07.58,0:43:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这件事是不行的 绝对不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.27,0:43:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 祥子大人的妹妹是我才对!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.13,0:43:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像祐巳说的那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:16.85,0:43:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊 爱丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.88,0:43:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.00,0:43:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:32.64,0:43:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被不熟悉的男人抱住…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.45,0:43:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是努力地撑了下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.02,0:43:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜呢 爱丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.74,0:43:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能上莉莉安的话 就算当不成祥子大人的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.26,0:43:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还可以和祐巳同学成为好朋友的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.23,0:43:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.52,0:43:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做朋友的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.68,0:43:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始不也可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.04,0:44:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 姐姐大人是不会让给你的~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:04.60,0:44:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝 我们也乐意和你成为朋友呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:09.40,0:44:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:11.95,0:44:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照 爱丽丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:14.71,0:44:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好相处吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:21.76,0:44:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了 各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:25.37,0:44:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那么今天就到这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:34.12,0:44:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…花寺的学生会长究竟是哪位呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.26,0:44:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是药师寺同学他们吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:44.95,0:44:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经从学生会引退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.43,0:44:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是监督者或者说是顾问的角色吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.95,0:44:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会不会是小林同学?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:53.75,0:44:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是会计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:55.24,0:44:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下三人 那么到底谁是学生会长呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:59.14,0:45:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位要不要来竞猜一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.91,0:45:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 多失礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.27,0:45:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办事不周请多多见谅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:08.70,0:45:12.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是今年花寺学院高中的学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:13.14,0:45:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:15.68,0:45:17.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.66,0:45:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦~~~~~!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.38,0:45:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 一直都瞒着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:29.25,0:45:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到祐巳同学的弟弟是学生会长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:32.87,0:45:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是出人意料的发展呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:35.23,0:45:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好歹我也是他姐姐 却连这么重要的事都不告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:40.54,0:45:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒他也有自己的难言之隐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:45.18,0:45:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是这样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.32,0:45:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去问问他不说的理由吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:49.77,0:45:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟你是个当姐姐的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.97,0:45:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:54.14,0:45:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然姐姐大人也这么说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.80,0:46:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳 今天谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.61,0:46:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了你 这次才能平安地度过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:17.17,0:46:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:19.18,0:46:21.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是表现出色呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:35.59,0:46:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来该是祐巳当个好姐姐的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.81,0:46:46.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一直瞒到现在?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.59,0:46:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没隐瞒啊 只是没说罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:52.10,0:46:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是自己站出来当候选人的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.70,0:46:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:56.68,0:46:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是柏木同学任命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.58,0:47:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我是个毫无实权的学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.91,0:47:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.55,0:47:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像是有权力的样子吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:10.45,0:47:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才没说啊 感觉有点凄惨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:18.88,0:47:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐麒你希望能做得像柏木同学一样吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:27.26,0:47:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用勉强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.84,0:47:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有权力的学生会长 这也不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.29,0:47:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我成为祥子的妹妹之后也曾一度十分烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.75,0:47:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己能否做好祥子大人的妹妹之类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.62,0:47:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 最后也只能做些能力所及的而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:55.14,0:47:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祐巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.80,0:47:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.59,0:48:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变坚强了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:01.89,0:48:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.07,0:48:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我都有些着急了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:20.38,0:48:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花寺的学园祭 能成功举办就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:26.25,0:48:27.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经满是秋意的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:28.66,0:48:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚时分 会有凉爽的微风吹过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.09,0:48:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然发生的大抵是些如身边拂过的微风般的琐事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.88,0:48:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仍旧会触动我们的心弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.82,0:48:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人时而叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.96,0:48:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时而落下泪来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:02.52,0:51:06.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个一年级的女孩开始跟在我的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:06.43,0:51:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然那个女孩十分地崇拜着我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:09.82,0:51:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是想成为祐巳同学的妹妹呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:11.94,0:51:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:13.09,0:51:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为祐巳同学和那个女孩不合适
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:15.20,0:51:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎? 是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.66,0:51:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打算收她当妹妹的话 还是先说清楚比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.24,0:51:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让对方有所期待后才拒绝 对两人都是一种不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:23.81,0:51:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么做呢? 祐巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.65,0:51:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着花寺学园祭的接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:28.07,0:51:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认妹妹的事情朝着意想不到的方向发展了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:27.08,0:51:31.96,next,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)}{\pos(757,420)}凉风飒飒
